  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Highlight Identifiers</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-style:normal;">When you select a specific word</text><text styleclass="Image Caption">, </text><text styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-style:normal;">it shows you all the places this word is used, this is case sensitive.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Highlight words.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The color for the highlights can be set in the Tools/Options dialog under the Environment/Fonts and Colors node. The X# specific colors all start with the text &quot;X#&quot;</para>
  </body>
